<%= provide(:body_id, 'components') %>
<%= provide(:result, '系统说明') %>

<div class="container-fluid content-wrapper">
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <button type="button" class="close hidden-phone" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
        <h1>出口标识信息</h1>

        <div class="row-fluid hidden-desktop hidden-phone">
          <div class="span12">
            <p>
              出口原始信息是由飞思达所提供的测试数据中提取，为了方便同后台维护部门核对，可添加相应的备注信息进行关联。<br/>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p></p>

        <p class="hidden-phone">
          <a class="btn btn-info btn-large pull-right">详细指南请猛击此处 &raquo;</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <ul class="breadcrumb">
        <li>
          <a href="/">
            <i class="radmin-icon radmin-home"></i>
            首页
          </a>
          <span class="divider">/</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/export/flag">
            <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
            出口标识
          </a>
          <span class="divider">/</span>
        </li>
        <li class="active">
          <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
          更新出口标识
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <form class="well form-horizontal" action="/export/mdf" method="get">
        <div class="row-fluid hidden-desktop hidden-phone">
          <div class="span12">
            <h4 class="title">出口标识资料修改</h4>

            <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
            <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-radmin">
              <thead>
              <tr>
                <th style="text-align:center;">出口编号</th>
                <th style="text-align:center;">出口名称</th>
                <th style="text-align:center;">操作选项</th>
              </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td style="text-align:center;">
                  <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= @en.id %>">
                  <%=  @en.alias %>
                </td>
                <td style="text-align:center;">
                  <%= text_field_tag :name, @en.name, :class => 'input-xlarge' %>
                </td>
                <td style="text-align:center;">
                  <button class="btn btn-info" type="submit">
                    更 新
                  </button>
                </td>
              </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <h4 class="title">名言警句</h4>

      <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <blockquote>
        <p>
          当一切似乎毫无希望时，我看着切石工人在他的石头上，敲击了上百次，而不见任何裂痕出现。
          但在第一百零一次时，石头被劈成两半。我体会到，并非那一击，而是前面的敲打使它裂开。
        </p>
        <small class="pull-right">贾柯·瑞斯</small>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>